preference.name: SC_ExportOptionSet_List
preference.preference_description: Defines the list of Export Option Sets applicable for briefcase and non briefcase Design Data Exchange and is displayed in the "Overview" tab of the "Exchange View" in the Supplier Collaboration application. User must have value(s) for this preference to perform forward trip for Design Data Exchange. Option sets applicable for briefcase export should have prefix "bcz_". Option sets applicable for non briefcase should have prefix "nonbcz_". Option sets applicable for managed briefcase should have prefix "mngdbcz_".
